DescDetail: <<

It makes it easy to change colors, title, font and geometry of a
running xterm, as well as to report the current settings of the
aforementioned properties.

Window manipulations de-/iconify, raise/lower, maximize/restore and
reset are also supported.

To complete the feature set; xtermcontrol lets advanced users issue
any xterm control sequence of their choosing.
<<